Script,Drury
setDealerCode(`

# convention-card:
# auction-filter: Note...:Reverse.drury

# Reverse Drury

dealer south
produce 1000

Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Calm-Opponents
# Defines calmOpps
Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/TP
# Defines tpNorth and tpSouth

# South passes
sPasses = tpSouth<12 and hcp(south)<11 and shape(south,any xxxx -any 9xxx -any 8xxx -any 7xxx -any 6xxx)

# Avoid a NT opener
nt =  hcp(north)>14 and hcp(north)<18 and shape(north,any 4333+any 4432+any 5332)

nMin = tpNorth==12 and hcp(north)==11
nSpades  = nMin ? spades(north)>5 : spades(north)>4
nHearts  = nMin ? hearts(north)>5 : hearts(north)>4
majorFit = (nSpades and spades(south)>2) or (nHearts and hearts(south)>2) and not nt
nRange = tpNorth>11 and hcp(north)>10 and hcp(north)<20

nOpens = majorFit and nRange and shape(north,any 6xxx+any 5xxx-any 65xx-any 55xx)

# Now do it
sPasses and nOpens and calmOpps

action
average "HCP North " hcp(north),
average "TP North  " tpNorth,
average "HCP South " hcp(south),
average "TP South  " tpSouth,

`,"S",true)
Script
Button,Drury,\n\
--- Drury\n\
After P (P) 1M (P)ï¼Œ2!C is Drury or Reverse Drury.\n\
2!C asks about the opener's hand.\n\
Drury:  2!D denies game interest and 2M shows game interest.\n\
Reverse Drury: 2!D shows some game interest and 2M denies game interest.\n\
%Drury%
